    <svcman/>
    <svcproc svcproctype="describe" graphiccount="0">
        <title>Ether Start</title>
        <para>When activated, the ether start system injects a measured amount of ether into the engine intake system to
            assist cold weather starting. The system will only function if the engine temperature is less than
            approximately 4.4&#176;C (40&#176;F).
        </para>
    </svcproc>
